OL,5,G0200 Yorkshire Great and Small with Dan
OL,6,G     and Helen
OL,7,     FThe duo follows in the footsteps
OL,8,     Fof James Herriot, exploring the
OL,9,     Fnatural beauty and uncovering
OL,10,     Fhidden delights of Swaledale and
OL,11,     FWensleydale along the Herriot Way.
